title: RAZ Vape TN9000 Disposable
description:
RAZ Vape with Battery Indicator, 5% Nicotine

Introducing the RAZ TN9000 by - a vaping experience like no other. This innovative device is equipped with a high-definition screen, customizable airflow, and an astonishing 9000 puffs per charge, transporting you to a vaping future that feels straight out of the year 3000.
Strawberry Ice:

Enjoy the sweetness of ripe red strawberries combined with an
energizing blast of icy coolness. It’s so berry cool!
Blue Razz Ice:

A happy fusion of tart blue raspberries and iced menthol, for a
frosty, berry-filled vape experience to remember.
Triple Berry Ice:

Find yourself immersed in a medley of luscious berries,
including succulent strawberries and juicy blueberries, all dipped in a frosty chill.
Dragon Fruit Lemonade:

A tropical cyclone of exotic dragon fruit supercharged with lemonade, for a tantalizing vaping sensation.
Cactus Jack:

Each puff is full of the unique flavor of cactus, delivering a refreshingly unconventional prickly vaping encounter.
Miami Mint:

It’s a Magic City Puff Party, featuring a cool minty South Beach breeze that's perfect for those seeking a hip mint-flavored vape.
Night Crawler:

Dive into this mysterious vape blend, offering a rich, deep flavor profile that will keep you intrigued puff after puff.
Experience the tangy allure of this fruity vape blend, featuring a tantalizing mix of sourness and tartness.
Strawberry Shortcake:

This classic dessert experience in vapor form features sweet strawberries and creamy cake layers that blend together for a perfectly delectable treat.
Cherry Lemon:

It’s time to enjoy tart cherries and zingy lemon simultaneously in this vibrant and mouth watering vape.
Graham Twist:

The comforting aroma and taste of sweet graham cracker crust, makes for a comforting and indulgent vape.
Blueberry Watermelon:

A delightful combo of ripe mountain blueberries and juicy garden fresh watermelon that delivers a super fruity vape fusion.
Mango Colada:

The luscious taste of mango meets creamy coconut, reminiscent of a pina colada in paradise.
Citronnade:

A zesty lemonade taste with an added blast of citrusy goodness. You’ll love its vibrant and thirst-quenching flavor profile.
Grape Ice:

You have to try this frozen grape sensation, drenched in a cool menthol breeze for a memorable vape experience.
Polar Ice:

You’ll feel like you are on top of the world with this pure menthol delight! It’s an intensely icy sensation that's perfect for those who search for that arctic blast.
Watermelon Ice:

Jump into the juicy natural sweetness of sun ripened watermelon enhanced with a chilled menthol finish. This revitalizing and fruity vape could easily become your favorite.
Banana Coconut:
Indulge in the tropical paradise of Banana Coconut, where the sweet, creamy notes of ripe bananas blend seamlessly with the luscious, exotic essence of coconut.
Blue Raz Cotton Clouds:
Immerse yourself in the whimsical world of Blue Raz Cotton Clouds, a delightful concoction that captures the essence of plump blue raspberries. This vape offers a burst of tangy sweetness reminiscent of your favorite blue raspberry candy, all enveloped in the airy fluffiness of cotton candy.
Orange Raspberry:
Experience the vibrant fusion of citrus and berry with Orange Raspberry, a flavor symphony that marries the zesty kick of ripe oranges with the juicy succulence of tart raspberries.
Peach Grapefruit:
Peach Grapefruit is a delightful combination of sweet ripe peaches and savory grapefruit, for a balanced fruit-filled vape vibe.
Pineapple Passionfruit Guava:
Take a tropical vape escape with Pineapple Passionfruit Guava! This bright blend of exotically intertwined fruit delivers a burst of sunshine. You’ll love the sweet, tart, and aromatic notes of this paradise-inspired vape.
Tobacco:
The timeless sophistication of Tobacco is yours! The rich, robust flavor of this vape features deep, smoky notes of fine, aged tobacco leaves, giving you a super satisfying vaping experience.
White Gummy Watermelon:
White Gummy Watermelon brings a playful twist on tasty fresh watermelon with the sweetness of white gummy candies too! This whimsically fruity vape captures the essence of summer days and nights gone by.
Clear:
The Clear vape flavor provides a lighter menthol taste with every puff. This essentially flavorless vape is just the ticket for adult vapers that enjoy no added sweetness. Finally, the satisfying light menthol kick on the finish provides a straightforward and unadulterated vaping experience.
Georgia Peach:
This vape delivers the natural flavor of sun-kissed, tree ripened Georgia peaches straight from the orchard. This flavor profile is sweet and juicy, so you can revel in the warmth and comfort of a Southern summer day with each puff.
Sour Mango Pineapple

:
You will dig the smooth and delicious pineapple flavor and sour punch of mango goodness from the first taste. Enjoy this refreshing combo all day and all night.
Black Cherry Peach:

Hold the essence of black cherries and ripe peaches in your hand as you enjoy the sweet and tart flavor explosion! It’s peachy!
Tropical Storm (Cherry Lime Grapefruit):

A flashy blast of flavor with every puff. Once discovered this “soft drink” flavor created a “tropical storm” of popularity. Best of all? No calories!
*Seasonal Flavor Limited Time* Apple Cinnamon
-
The comforting warmth of cinnamon with the crispness of sweet ripe apples, makes for a flavorful vape that evokes the appealing aroma of freshly baked apple and cinnamon muffins. If you are seeking a delightful balance of spice and fruit, this is the one.
*Seasonal Flavor Limited Time* Pumpkin
- This vape captures the spirit of fall with its earthy pumpkin flavor. Expect a smooth and velvety vape that brings the warmth of the Autumn season directly to your palate.
flavors_description:
*NEW* Dream Edition Violet (Grape Strawberry):
Glide right into the sparkly fusion of grape sweetness with the delicate essence of vine ripened strawberries. This desirable vape will tease your taste buds with its rich, fruity profile.
*NEW* Dream Edition Ruby (Cherry Strawberry Raspberry):
Experience a symphony of flavor with this creative blend. The sweet taste of cherries, garden fresh strawberries, and tangy raspberries join perfectly for a vibrant, party vape that's perfect for
girls night out
.
*NEW* Dream Edition Vicky (Pink Lemonade):
Quench your thirst with the zesty appeal of Pink Lemonade. This citrusy delight combines tart lemons with a pinch of sugar, and fits perfectly inside your pocket or purse.
*NEW* Dream Edition Tiffany (Kiwi Watermelon):
Get all dolled up and dig the tropical allure of Kiwi Watermelon, where juicy kiwis crash into luscious red watermelon on a “first date” filled with sweet and tangy dreams of vape love.

Overcharging Protection Mechanisms

        1. CBD:
           - 1 if the product contains CBD/THC.
           - 0 if the product contains nicotine or no CBD/THC.
           - 2 if the product contains both nicotine and CBD/THC.

        2. Synthetic Nicotine (TFN):
           - 1 if the product contains synthetic nicotine (phrases like "Synthetic", "Tobacco-free nicotine", "Non-tobacco nicotine", etc.).
           - 0 if it does not contain synthetic nicotine.
           - "Metatine" if it contains Metatine.
           - "Unknown" if synthetic nicotine status cannot be determined.

        3. Nicotine-free (NF):
           - 0 if the product contains nicotine.
           - 0* if there are multiple nicotine levels with a nicotine-free option (0 mg or 0%) available.
           - 1 if the product is free of nicotine (i.e. only offers 0 mg or 0% options).
           - "Unknown" if nicotine-free status cannot be determined.

        Return three key:value pairs separated by commas such as (CBD:0, TFN:"Unknown", NF:1) with your reasoning in a separate section:
         (CBD:0, TFN:0, NF:0)

Reasoning:
The product contains 5% nicotine, which is a standard nicotine concentration. There is no mention of CBD or THC in the description. Therefore, the product contains nicotine but no CBD/THC. The product does not contain synthetic nicotine as there is no mention of phrases like "Synthetic", "Tobacco-free nicotine", "Non-tobacco nicotine", etc. The product is not nicotine-free as it contains 5% nicotine.

title: Grape Minty O's MiNTOPiA Vape 6000 Puffs
image_alt_text: Grape Minty O's MiNTOPiA Vape 6000 Puffs
description:
MiNTOPiA Vape 6000 Puffs
Vape

Introducing the MiNTOPiA 6000, a cutting-edge vaping device combining advanced features and various flavorful options. With its 10mL pre-filled E-Liquid capacity, you can enjoy extended vaping sessions without frequent refills. The 5% (50mg) nicotine strength is satisfying, catering to both seasoned vapers and those transitioning from traditional cigarettes.
Equipped with a powerful 500mAh Type-C rechargeable battery, the MiNTOPiA 6000 ensures long-lasting performance, allowing you to vape throughout the day without interruption. But what sets this device apart is its standout feature: the digital display screen. With this innovative addition, you can effortlessly monitor your battery life and keep track of the remaining e-liquid. Say goodbye to surprises and enjoy uninterrupted vaping pleasure with precise control over your device's vital aspects.
To enhance your vaping experience, MiNTOPiA offers a range of tantalizing flavors. Choose from Peach Minty O's, Strawberry Minty O's, Blueberry Minty O's, Grape Minty O's, or Peppermint Minty O's. Each flavor is perfectly crafted, delivering a unique blend of fruity sweetness and refreshing minty notes. With the MiNTOPiA 6000 and its digital display screen, you can savor these flavors easily, knowing your battery life and e-liquid levels are at your fingertips. Experience the ultimate vaping companion with the MiNTOPiA 6000, where innovation meets flavor.
Contains Tobacco-Free Nicotine

Puff Count: Approximately 6000
500mAh Type-C Rechargeable Battery - USB-C Charging Cord Not Included
Digital Battery & eLiquid Display Screen
Mesh Coil Heating Element

Strawnana Freeze
: Strawnana Freeze offers a frosty smooth blend of island bananas and hand picked strawberries. It tastes like it was chilled to perfection, as it delivers its refreshing icy blast! This is an invigorating vape that's just right for cooling off on hot summer days, or chilling out anytime.
Watermelon Bubblegum
: Capture the essence of warm summer months with this juicy watermelon flavor all wrapped up in sweet bubblegum. You’ll enjoy a playful vape experience that's as refreshing as it is delightful, and brings back memories too of bubblegum days gone by.
Melonberry Ice
: What do you get when you combine the sweetness of ripe melons with the tartness of mixed berries, all chilled to perfection with a frosty menthol finish? You get Melonberry Ice, for a refreshing and fruity vape that's the perfect cool and invigorating puff.
Fuji Apple Freeze
: Juicy Fuji Apple Freeze is a crisp and refreshing vape flavor enhanced with a frosty menthol kick. It delivers a revitalizing blast of flavor that's perfect for an energizing pick-me-up.
Black Ice
: Black Ice will tantalize your taste buds with its bold and mysterious blend of dark berries, infused with a cool menthol breeze. This super smooth vape experience is awesome and invigorating.
Miami Mint
:
The vibrant pulse of Miami comes through with this slick mint flavor, where cool mint meets the energy of South Beach. It will leave you revitalized and feeling super chic.
Sweet Tartz
: Gather ‘round vape lovers! Sweet Tartz is making the scene with a big blast of fruity sweetness and tangy fruits. It’s reminiscent of your favorite candy from your youth! You’ll love this nostalgic, fun vape experience that's sweet and rewarding.
Sour Peach Rings
: Dazzle your taste buds with this sweet and sour peach flavor. It’s infused with a sour twist reminiscent of those popular gummy candies, and delivers a mouth-puckering puff party vape that's just the ticket for sour candy lovers.
Strawmelon Burst
: Strawmelon Burst comes on the scene combining juicy sweet strawberries and the popular taste of watermelon. A vibrantly fruity vape that’s just bursting with flavor!
Prickly Pear Peach
: Prickly Pear Peach tastes like it just came off the cactus! It offers a desert blend of exotic prickly pear cactus flavor, and tree ripened peaches. It’s a unique vape experience that is intriguing and delicious.
Aloe Grape
:
Discover a one of a kind fusion of succulent grapes and soothing aloe vera that’s perfectly balanced to hint you with a delightful blend of fruity sweetness and fragrant herbal notes from start to finish.
Nana Taffy Ice
: Grandmother would be proud to see you vaping this flavor, because it offers an indulgent vape experience with its blend of ripe bananas and sweet salt water taffy. It feels like you’re back on the Jersey shore, as you enjoy this unusually tasty vape treat. Finally it is chilled to perfection with a frosty menthol finish.
Soul Mint
: Recharge your soul as you indulge in this smooth minty vape that’s as calming as a gentle ocean breeze. You feel its clean, pure puff power as it completely relaxes and recharges you puff after puff.

title: Lost Mary OS5000 Vape | Black Strawnana (Luster Edition)
specifications_section:
This e-cigarette liquid is a great choice for those looking to enjoy vaping with a long-lasting bottle. Featuring a 13ml capacity and up to 5000 estimated puffs, your device will last you significantly longer than other liquids currently on the market. The 650mAh rechargeable battery is incredibly powerful and performs excellently with every puff. Furthermore, the mesh coil helps evenly distribute heat through the device, so you experience a more robust flavor from each puff. And, of course, this e-liquid comes in 50mg (5%) strength for a reliable performance every time. It should be noted that this product does not include a USB-C charger, which must be purchased separately, making it important you check compatibility before purchasing one.

This e-liquid offers great value for money and excellent features that make it ideal for any vaper. The 13ml bottle and high-capacity rechargeable battery make it perfect for long trips or extended sessions while also lasting longer than most other options on the market. The powerful mesh coil ensures even heat distribution throughout each puff and makes for delightful flavor in each draw of vapor too! Lastly, with 5% strength available, you can count on consistent quality no matter how often you vape.E-liquid capacity: 13ml5000 puffs approx.650mAh rechargeable batteryMesh coil50mg (5%) strengthUSB-C charger not included
description:
The Lost Mary Elf Bar OS5000 Puff Disposable Vape is a remarkable piece of engineering, packing performance, and style into one neat package. Featuring a candy-shell and flagon design, with 37 vibrant flavors to choose from, it’s the perfect choice for both casual and advanced vapers alike. The OS5000 offers an impressive 5000-puff lifespan, so you don’t have to worry about constantly running out of juice. To top it off, the device is equipped with a battery indicator that changes color to signify charge level – green (high), blue (medium), or red (low) – meaning you can always make sure your device is adequately charged before hitting it. In addition, it can be recharged with a standard USB-C cable if your battery does run low. Altogether this vape has made its mark in the vaping market, appealing to all types of users due to its versatility and efficiency.

title: Apple Peach HQD Cuvie Plus 1200 Puff Disposable Vape
image_alt_text: Apple Peach HQD Cuvie Plus 1200 Puff Disposable Vape
description:
Introducing the HQD Cuvie Vape 1200: A Sleek and Powerful Vaping Companion

Experience vaping like never before with the HQD Cuvie Plus 1200 Disposable Vape, a modern day portable vaping solution that combines sleek design, exceptional performance, and unparalleled convenience. Designed with both beginners and seasoned vapers in mind, this compact and stylish device boasts a satisfying vaping experience that will leave you craving more.
With its ergonomic design, the HQD Cuvie Plus 1200 Disposable Vape fits perfectly in the palm of your hand, providing a natural grip and easy handling. It's ideal for on-the-go vaping, and fits into pockets, purses, or backpacks without adding bulk.
Equipped with a powerful 950mAh built-in battery, the HQD Cuvie Plus 1200 Disposable Vape ensures long-lasting and without frequent recharging. You'll enjoy uninterrupted pleasure throughout the day.
Choose the HQD Cuvie Plus 1200 Disposable Vape and take your vaping experience to new heights. The HQD Cuvie Plus 1200 Disposable Vape will exceed your expectations and provide you with ultimate satisfaction every day. Embrace the future of vaping with the HQD Cuvie Plus 1200 Disposable Vape.
flavors_description:
Nuts Tobacco:
A robust blend of earthy tasting tobacco leaves with a perfect puff of roasted nuts, delivering a truly smooth and satisfying vape experience.
Ice Mint:
Cool and refreshing, this invigorating combo combines icy menthol with a blast of minty freshness, leaving a crisp and soothing sensation on your tongue.
Black Ice:
A magical fusion of dark fruits and chilled menthol, this vape flavor creates a smooth and puzzlingly sweet experience.
Tobacco:
This vape captures the timeless essence of pure tobacco leaves. The result is a rich and full-bodied taste that satisfies traditional tobacco enthusiasts 100%.
Sky Mint:
The sky's the limit with this heavenly blend of mint and spearmint, offering a cool and airy flavor that leaves a revitalizing cloud breeze in your wake.
Blueberry Raspberry:
Indulge in the succulent sweetness of ripe blueberries, happily combined with the tangy tongue teasing taste of fresh raspberries, resulting in a delightful and fruity vape.
Lush Ice:
A alluring mixture of juicy watermelon and icy menthol, this vape flavor has an ice cold blast that leaves you feeling so fresh.
Strawberry:
The naturally pure delight of sun-ripened strawberries delivers a burst of irresistibly sweet and juicy flavor that’s so fresh and summery.
Blueberry Lemonade:
“Sip” on the perfect summertime vape! Zesty lemonade is infused with sweet ripe blueberries, creating a tantalizing sweet and sour combination.
Grapey:
Unleash the stunning grape flavor in this vape, and let the heavenly notes dominate your taste buds with each juicy inhale.
Banana Ice:
Jump into creamy richness that only ripe bananas can offer. Blended with an icy coolness resulting in a smooth and refreshing vape that may even transport you to tropical dream locations
Strawberry Banana:
The perfect balance of luscious strawberries and creamy bananas takes center stage, performing together to create a fruity, velvety blend.
Tres Leche:
Taste this dessert-inspired vape flavor delight, capturing the essence of tres leches cake with its creamy and caramelized undertones.
Rainbow:
Set sail on a vibrant journey, as a medley of fruity flavors dances on your taste buds, creating a smiling rainbow of sweet and tangy goodness.
Apple Peach:
Savor the beautiful taste of freshly picked apples and ripe peaches. A juicy and refreshing vape that embodies the root of orchard-fresh fruits.
